- You will create WebSite model and table in database.
   - Your fields: 
         - id
         - domain
         - requestDuration
         - HtmlTagCount
         - url
         - status 
         - created_at
         - updated_at
- You will create CrawlerController
     - This endpoint will validate request and save record with waiting status
     - If validation successfull this endpoint will return 200 response and with this message 'We are crawling website now.'
     - If validation failled this endpoint will return validation error message.     
     - This endpoint will create a message.
     - We will use Symfony Messenger Component for crawling process.
     - This endpoint will create a message. example name: CrawlMessage
     - We will write CrawlMessageHandler. This handler will be crawl web site and update status and related fields in database.
     - Use default DoctrineMessenger
     - Write CrawlerService and use this service in CrawlMessageHandler.
     - Write test for CrawlerService.     
